---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Notebook
description: 个人技术笔记与工程实践记录，按主题维护学习材料、工程笔记和长期可复用的知识入口。
permalink: /index.html
breadcrumbs:
  - title: Notebook
    url: /index.html
toc:
  - id: directories
    text: 主题目录
  - id: recent
    text: 最近更新
---
<section id="directories">
  <h2><span class="section-index">1</span><span class="section-title">主题目录</span></h2>
  <div class="directory-grid">
    {% for directory in notebook.topDirectories %}
      <a class="directory-card" href="{{ directory.permalink | relativeUrl(page.url) }}">
        <strong>{{ directory.title }}</strong>
        <span>{{ directory.children.length }} 个子目录 · {{ directory.articles.length }} 篇直属文章</span>
      </a>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>

<section id="recent">
  <h2><span class="section-index">2</span><span class="section-title">最近更新</span></h2>
  <ol class="article-list">
    {% for article in notebook.articles | limit(14) %}
      <li>
        <a href="{{ article.url | relativeUrl(page.url) }}">{{ article.title }}</a>
        <span>{{ article.category }} · {{ article.date | readableDate }}</span>
      </li>
    {% endfor %}
  </ol>
</section>
